### CodeMentor AI Companion API Tests
### Make sure the companion app is running on port 8000

### Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

###

### Root Endpoint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

###

### Get Supported Languages
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/supported-languages

###

### Analyze TypeScript Code
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "typescript",
  "code": "const userName = 'john'; var count = 0; function getUserName() { return userName; }",
  "fileName": "test.ts",
  "framework": "react"
}

###

### Analyze Python Code
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "python",
  "code": "def get_user_name():\n    user_name = 'john'\n    return user_name",
  "fileName": "test.py"
}

###

### Ask LLM Question
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Why should I use camelCase instead of snake_case in TypeScript?",
  "context": {
    "language": "typescript",
    "code": "const user_name = 'john';"
  }
}

###

### Ask LLM Question (No Context)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What are the benefits of consistent naming conventions?"
}

###

### Get Language Rules
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/rules/typescript

###

### Get Language Rules (Python)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/rules/python

###

### Test Invalid Language
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/rules/invalid-language

###

### Test Invalid Analysis Request (Missing Code)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/analysis/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "language": "typescript",
  "fileName": "test.ts"
}

###

### Test Invalid LLM Request (Missing Question)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "context": {
    "language": "typescript"
  }
} 